01:09:30.791 --> 01:09:32.626
<font color="white"><i>and getting jealous</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>of other people's success.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

933
01:09:32.710 --> 01:09:34.295
<font color="white">start living more constructively</font><font color="white"></font>

934
01:09:35.379 --> 01:09:36.839
<font color="white">and productively from now on.</font><font color="white"></font>

935
01:09:42.553 --> 01:09:43.470
<font color="white">Okay?</font><font color="white"></font>

936
01:09:48.225 --> 01:09:50.311
<font color="white">Why the hell does my life</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">have to please you. sir?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

937
01:09:57.484 --> 01:09:59.403
<font color="white">You crazy bastard! What are you doing?</font><font color="white"></font>

938
01:10:10.289 --> 01:10:11.457
<font color="white">Bravo!</font><font color="white"></font>

939
01:10:15.252 --> 01:10:16.086
<font color="white">Sorry.</font><font color="white"></font>

940
01:10:19.840 --> 01:10:23.135
<font color="white">WE ARE ALL TRYING HERE</font><font color="white"></font>

941
01:10:42.321 --> 01:10:43.572
{\an8}<font color="white">Did you get beaten up?</font><font color="white"></font>

942
01:10:43.656 --> 01:10:45.074
{\an8}<font color="white">Then what's with the cast?</font><font color="white"></font>

943
01:10:45.157 --> 01:10:47.284
{\an8}<font color="white">Hey. Dong-man!</font><font color="white"></font>

944
01:10:48.285 --> 01:10:49.995
{\an8}<font color="white">I said go and print it out!</font><font color="white"></font>

945
01:10:50.079 --> 01:10:52.790
{\an8}<font color="white">I feel for her.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">but she has to handle it on her own.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

946
01:10:53.457 --> 01:10:57.294
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>How should we describe the emotion</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>you feel when you get nosebleeds?</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

947
01:10:57.378 --> 01:10:58.212
{\an8}<font color="white">You bastard!</font><font color="white"></font>

948
01:10:58.295 --> 01:11:01.340
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>You know what I mean.</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>He ruins everything wherever he goes.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

949
01:11:01.423 --> 01:11:03.092
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>You're not allowed to come here anymore.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

950
01:11:03.175 --> 01:11:06.303
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Adults call it cutting ties.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

951
01:11:06.387 --> 01:11:08.847
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Cutting ties as a group</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>is called bullying. you bastard!</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

952
01:11:08.931 --> 01:11:11.892
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Why do you all find Director Hwang</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>so hard to deal with?</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

953
01:11:11.976 --> 01:11:13.978
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>How do people gain power?</i></font><font color="white"></font>

954
01:11:15.813 --> 01:11:17.189
{\an8}<font color="white">Maybe if you love someone…</font><font color="white"></font>

955
01:11:17.773 --> 01:11:19.441
{\an8}<font color="white">His heart would race.</font><font color="white"></font>

956
01:11:21.193 --> 01:11:26.198
{\an8}<font color="white">Subtitle translation by: Jenny Kim</font><font color="white"></font>
